      "text": "More than a century ago, U.S. Army veteran Sam Sabatino was wounded by German machine gun fire while serving in World War I. This week, I had the honor of presenting his family with the Purple Heart he earned.\n\nSam’s grandson, a Johnson County constituent, came to our office for",
