      "text": "Fifty years ago, the Army Corps of Engineers built Brookville Lake to help control flooding. Today, it’s one of eastern Indiana’s great outdoor destinations.\n\nOn summer weekends like this, Hoosiers and visitors from across the region come here to fish, boat, camp, and enjoy more https://t.co/FKxUTq82ZZ",
